%27s+Shadow\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div> \n<div role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Portals\" class=\"noprint portal plainlist tright\" style=\"margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 1em;border:solid #aaa 1px\">\n<ul style=\"display:table;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0.1em;max-width:175px;background:#f9f9f9;font-size:85%;line-height:110%;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold\">\n<li style=\"display:table-row\"><span style=\"display:table-cell;padding:0.2em;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/20px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg\" width=\"20\" height=\"28\" class=\"noviewer\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/30px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/41px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"1115\" data-file-height=\"1536\" /></span><span style=\"display:table-cell;padding:0.2em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em;vertical-align:middle\"><a href=\"/wiki/Portal:Children%27s_literature\" title=\"Portal:Children&#39;s literature\">Children's literature portal</a></span></li></ul></div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<table class=\"metadata plainlinks stub\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"background:transparent\"><tbody><tr><td><a href=\"/wiki/File:Castle_(color).svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Stub icon\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/Castle_%28color%29.svg/35px-Castle_%28color%29.svg.png\" width=\"35\" height=\"59\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/Castle_%28color%29.svg/53px-Castle_%28color%29.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/64/Castle_%28color%29.svg/70px-Castle_%28color%29.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"501\" data-file-height=\"839\" /></a></td><td><i>This article about a non-fiction histor